		<title>5 Important Lessons from FaceApp</title>
		<link>https://blog.andromo.com/2019/5-important-lessons-you-can-learn-from-faceapp/</link>
		<comments>https://blog.andromo.com/2019/5-important-lessons-you-can-learn-from-faceapp/#respond</comments>
